description:
When Nikki started acting out her parents were at the end of their ropes, the once bright well behaved high school Grad had gone wild in the last year and nothing they did seemed to curb her wayward ways.
Her father Stan thought of his old buddy Jeremy Ashton from his days in the Marines, Jeremy had always been a hard ass and Stan remembered that he was good at getting people to tow the line.
Only with his eldest daughter's best interest at heart he called up his old pal and decided it would be the best thing to do to leave her with the other man for the summer, maybe he could straighten her out before she left home for college.

Nikki wasn't sure what was going on in her body all she knew was that she needed something but not sure what. She loved teasing the boys in their small town getting a rise out of them as well as some of her teachers who couldn't seem to keep their eyes off her tits which had sprung up in the last year, now her parents were packing her off to some old friend..
